Hello and welcome to the Assembly Guide for the IMU Controlled RC Car project for Hack Club Fallout.

In this document, a step-by-step guide will be given for how to build this project.
Whenever any file is mentioned, it can either be found in this document or elsewhere in the repository. Links to the parts, for example, can be found within the BOM (Bill of Materials).
Any firmware or files (such as STEP files for the car case) will be provided with a guide on where they are within the repository (i.e. Group -> SubGroup -> FileName)

